title: Google voicemail box won't load voicemails
content: Recently my Google voicemail box won't load my voicemails. I keep getting the message "couldn't load voicemail". I'm using it over 4G like always. When I access my voicemail box using *86 the voicemails are there and I can listen to them. It seems like the voicemail app isn't working. Both my app and phone are all current on any updates. I tried clearing the app's cache but that didn't help.
